    <div class="section about align-left" id="about-section">
        <div class="fw">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col col-m-12 col-t-4 col-d-4">
            <div class="profile">
                <img src="images/works/small/id.jpg" alt="Nikos Tsigros - Web Developer Profile Photo" />
            </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col col-m-12 col-t-8 col-d-8">
            <div class="text-box">
                <h1>
                I'm Nikos Tsigros, <br />
                Web Developer from Greece.
                </h1>
                <p>
                I’m a Frontend Engineer with 7+ years of experience designing and building high-performance web applications. My main focus is React, Next.js, and modern frontend architecture — always striving for scalable solutions, clean UI/UX, accessibility, and best development practices.</p>
                <p>
I collaborate closely with clients to turn ideas into polished digital products, whether that’s a custom WordPress site or a fully responsive and interactive web platform.</p>
<p>
As I continue to grow, I’m expanding my skills into backend development and cloud-driven architectures — aiming to deliver complete, end-to-end solutions with strong engineering foundations.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bts">
                <a
                href="#works-section"
                class="btn extra"
                style="margin-right: 10px"
                >See My Work</a
                >
                <a href="#contact-section" class="btn extra">Contact Me</a>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div
