                    /></a>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="popup-0" class="popup-box mfp-fade mfp-hide">
                <div class="content">
                <div class="image">
                    <img src="images/works/tsigros-gym-booking-9.jpg" alt="Tsigkros Gym Booking App - Full Screen Preview" />
                </div>
                <div class="desc">
                    <div class="category">Web App</div>
                    <h3>Tsigkros Gym Booking App</h3>
                    <p>
                    Custom Design, Develop and Maintain an online booking website system for fitness studios, where the clients can register their account and book their monthly subscription to their desired fitness classes.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                    Technologies : Nextjs, React, Nodejs, MongoDB, Material UI, Styled Components, NextAuth
                    </p>
                    <a
                    href="https://photos.google.com/share/AF1QipNudcQ7i9nccL4bq-hFJd1CnNP6sZ_zxdphl_5x5cosBgSgZ4d_ugxWNGTsSY5BNQ?pli=1&key=cFhLY01EMEstSVhFMl90X09mOXJ1WDdXS3NWSnBR"
                    class="btn"
                    target="_blank"
                    >View Project</a
                    >
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            </div>
            <div
            class="col col-m-12 col-t-6 col-d-4 box-item f-wordpress"
            >
            <div class="item">
                <div class="desc">
                <div class="image">
                    <a href="#popup-1" class="has-popup"
                    ><img src="images/works/small/abc-edu-gr-small.jpg" alt="ABC EDU GR - Study and Family Counseling Center Website"
                    /></a>
                </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="popup-1" class="popup-box mfp-fade mfp-hide">
                <div class="content">
                <div class="image">
                    <img src="images/works/abc-edu-gr.png" alt="ABC EDU GR - Full Website Preview" />
                </div>
                <div class="desc">
                    <div class="category">Website</div>
                    <h3>ABC EDU GR</h3>
                    <p>
                    I developed the official website for ABC EDU GR, a Study and Family Counseling Center based in Palaio Faliro. The project included crafting a user-friendly interface, creating a responsive layout for all devices, and delivering a clean structure that effectively communicates the center’s educational and support services to parents and children.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                    Technologies : Wordpress
                    </p>
                    <a
                    href="https://abc.edu.gr"
                    class="btn"
                    target="_blank"
                    >View Project</a
